g.text: The formula edge of a conjunctive (<And>) or disjunctive (<Or>) expression,
an extension point for stripe skipping as well as specializations of the formula tag name in assertions and retractions.
Assertions and retractions contain zero or more formulas.
assertions and retractions have scope inference direction
and scope material implication as an attribute.
